  "prompt": "What are some best resume?",
  "response": "Here are some characteristics of the best resumes:\n\n1. Clear and Professional Layout\n- Clean, easy-to-read format\n- Consistent font and sizing\n- Appropriate white space\n- Aligned and organized sections\n\n2. Targeted Content\n- Tailored to specific job/industry\n- Highlights relevant skills and experiences\n- Uses keywords from job description\n- Quantifies achievements\n\n3. Strong Resume Sections\n- Clear contact information\n- Professional summary/objective\n- Work experience with accomplishments\n- Education details\n- Skills section\n- Relevant certifications\n\n4. Best Practices\n- Maximum 1-2 pages\n- No grammatical errors\n- Reverse chronological order\n- Use action verbs\n- Avoid personal pronouns\n\n5. Recommended Resume Types\n- Chronological Resume\n- Functional Resume\n- Combination/Hybrid Resume\n\n6. Modern Digital Considerations\n- ATS (Applicant Tracking System) friendly\n- PDF format\n- Mobile-friendly layout\n\n7. Industry-Specific Variations\n- Tech: Emphasize technical skills\n- Sales: Highlight achievements\n- Creative: Demonstrate portfolio\n- Academic: Detailed research/publications\n\nRemember, the best resume is one that effectively communicates your unique professional value.",
